    "The 'bestP lowV' strategy selects the best combination based on non-value criteria and calculated priority, maximizing strategic advantage while minimizing potential loss.",
    "It chooses the combination with the highest strategic priority and the lowest value among those with the optimal pattern.",
    "The 'random' strategy will execute a random action from the available options.",
